n你信個種信仰係對你好，要你自己克服<br />\n而唔係好似大部分嘅基督徒去依賴信仰"},{"pid":"5715067410a3580847cb48f41f331f658c185b5d","tid":335733,"uid":117365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T23:06:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最慘係有時啲人返教會崇拜係到喊係到叫 好似中邪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問佢地做乜喊 佢地話感動又話感覺到神係佢則邊 好恐佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最極端我都見過會暈低 未見過會嘔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4445023401464f433e6b40bf77329cd0e11e6a02","tid":335733,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T23:09:32.000Z","msg":"諗起我識三個唔同既耶撚女人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3個都一定要男朋友係耶撚<br />\n<br />\n1個正正常常好女仔，不過已經一段時間冇得拍拖，之前有一個佢又鐘意人地，人地又鐘意佢既男人出現，最後又因為宗教冇一齊<br />\n<br />\n第2個係怪人，佢同一個教會內既另一個怪人結左婚，兩公婆都神神化化到仆街<br />\n<br />\n第3個又係怪人，三十幾歲都仲a0，話自己有獨身恩賜，可以單身方便佢待奉主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，現實係日撚日追韓劇話韓仔點好點好"},{"pid":"8280a7fa913994b3d7db3c532b2ae705ffb12130","tid":335733,"uid":111354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T23:12:41.000Z","msg":"忍到有經濟能力即走"},{"pid":"50177181915962494b24c7792e6ccdc53c3d32aa","tid":335733,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T23:18:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>耶魔依個宗教根本係一個世紀大謊言<br />\n等我做左新世界既王之後一定消㓕依個邪教</blockquote><br />\n消左伊斯蘭先啦係都。。</blockquote><br />\n咪又係同一個神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n伊斯蘭個神都俾件垃圾搞到變哂質。。唔一樣</blockquote><br />\n咪又係同一個一神教"},{"pid":"ad0ff68dc99e9997a0bfd38b0737050a07440f93","tid":335733,"uid":129043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T23:18:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b7558daee7cb251e8b3668cc98b20b31ade456","tid":335733,"uid":36073,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T23:23:29.000Z","msg":"教會同宗教可以本身分開<br />\n但係因為教會係人建立出嚟，教會之間又會有唔同觀念衝突<br />\n所以，我覺得，到最後都其實係「人性」作弄<br />\n就咁我就冇信過任何宗教<br />\n<br />\n更何況，我老豆嘅家庭係耶撚家庭<br />\n阿嫲深信基督教<br />\n但係我阿嫲喺我老豆口中，係一個好自私嘅人<br />\n分化咗我老豆同其他兄姊，佢地齊齊去美國讀自己想要嘅書，喺嗰邊定居<br />\n唯獨要我老豆放棄後生嗰時嘅夢想，留喺香港負責家庭生意<br />\n生意到2000年初做唔掂，要倒閉<br />\n最終，我老豆成日喺到呻乜都冇晒<br />\n更因為阿嫲喺佢細個成日分化佢<br />\n結果老豆患上輕度精神病，要定時覆診食藥<br />\n<br />\n所以話，信教都唔會改變一樣野，「人性」<br />\n我細個阿嫲對我好，我都因為咁細個有祈禱<br />\n但係，我聽完老豆講之後<br />\n大個咗就唔再信教<br />\n亦都唔會聽耶撚親戚嘅甜言蜜語<br />\n<br />\n樓主要決裂，我一定撐你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9512fb53411c8117fc5382df50994be6ae03bd","tid":335733,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T23:25:24.000Z","msg":"個人意志行先啦 問問問"},{"pid":"b29246075739821635b668af80d13cae91903f5a","tid":335733,"uid":78396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T23:25:39.000Z","msg":"你屋企人有問題 唔關宗教事 <br />\n快d遠離佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ca50b8820294cde28ea11a42958e9e5c18dc15","tid":335733,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T23:34:18.000Z","msg":"你知唔知依家你要做咩？<br />\n<br />\n拎起個十字架燒鳩咗佢，然後離家出走"},{"pid":"f1a4120de66bc77789f926c960d0c9a7ff83246